    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You can download a package which can successfully install everything apart from the Notebook. We should make it clear why the Notebook isn't working, e.g. with a runtime check for the notebook static files, but we shouldn't completely cripple that file just because it doesn't work for the notebook. Especially since detecting the case to cripple it makes life more complicated.\n"
